title: TrendSYNC 3/28: Taylor Hawkins, Will Smith, John Eastman, Disney, Roman Abramovich
itunes:title: TrendSYNC 3/28: Taylor Hawkins, Will Smith, John Eastman, Disney, Roman Abramovich
description:
In this edition of TrendSYNC, Miles and Jacquis discuss the passing of Taylor Hawkins, the Chris Rock/Will Smith situation, A federal judge ordering John Eastman to release Jan. 6th emails, Disney vowing to help repeal the 'Don't Say Gay' Bill, and Roman Abramovich and Ukrainian peace negotiators suffering symptoms of poisoning.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
